{"tid":1077942,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑有人偷偷加速左時間","createTime":"2019-03-26T02:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T03:14:29.000Z","uid":54930,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04fa63c8e937f9357e22f791beb5242f50b51f8c","tid":1077942,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"點解2x歲既時間過得比1x歲快咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b4d2059b45cfa10c72d590c5507e9901ed2823","tid":1077942,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81cff97b47061304ca4acd98486e3f20122e339c","tid":1077942,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"左加速 右減速<br />\n其實冇多到"},{"pid":"7753901e2f66bb75529eb48c91478478056952e4","tid":1077942,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:56:37.000Z","msg":"made in heaven"},{"pid":"ef4d18077c436c2dd8fd69f8a0e9a3c3c9378ddd","tid":1077942,"uid":163743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"你知道得太多了"},{"pid":"74ff919ecf0791105ac6d059804fbe92bb9bb735","tid":1077942,"uid":82398,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"因為你日日等出糧望時間快啲過"},{"pid":"0ea9e3b648ac623b753f196711e9668d8b1a468d","tid":1077942,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6LyCC6jjcx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6LyCC6jjcx8&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=db8ff6a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6LyCC6jjcx8</a><br />\n2:20<br />\n個個人都會咁  唔係全世界就你一個架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad89ce0c8578ea54e87f2218c71c5fc0a833c735","tid":1077942,"uid":39608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"只會愈來愈快<br />\n<br />\n感覺時間一年過得比一年快，不是沒有根據的迷思（Myth）。早在 1975 年，美國辛辛納提大學（University of Cincinnati）化學工程系退休教授 Robert Lemlich 就發表相關研究，指出人對於時間的看法，是基於生活經歷的比例；小孩 4 歲，一年是他生命中的 25%，但到了 40 歲，一年便是生命的 2.5%，所以，對於「一年」的時間感覺上比較短。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地必須好好活在當下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}